Subject: Re: [VB] Child Car Seats and Ventage Bus

The Z Bed in a '65 Westy is secured to the floor with
two bolts. When i was dating a girl who had a child i
used those bolts to mount seatbelts. I am not sure
what you would do with two of them rascals though!

Sean
'65 Westfalia

